				<div class="comment-body"><p>You cannot submit works for the Hugo Awards. Read <a href="../index.html?page_id=191" rel="nofollow">Submissions</a> on our web site and <a href="../index.html?page_id=4" rel="nofollow">The Voting System</a> for a full description of the process of getting the awards.</p>
<p>The short version is that the members of the annual World Science Fiction Convention nominate works, and also vote on the final Award selection.</p>
</div>

