				<div class="comment-body"><p>The site worked for me at 20:07 on 2015/07/30, about twenty minutes after you posted your message.</p>
<p>Questions about the 2015 Hugo Awards voting should go directly to the <a href="mailto:hugoadmin@sasquan.org" rel="nofollow">2015 Hugo Awards Administrators</a>, because they are the ones who are actually running the 2015 Hugo Awards. Anything sent to TheHugoAwards.org will simply be forwarded to them. Those of us here at TheHugoAwards.org are not the ones running the current Worldcon&#8217;s web site or the Hugo Awards voting at their web site, so we can&#8217;t directly do anything about voting issues with the current year&#8217;s Awards.</p>
</div>

