				<div class="comment-body"><p>How is it that a magazine is able to claim it is &#8220;Hugo-nominated&#8221; when it never appeared in the official list of nominees?</p>
</div>

				<div class="reply">
				<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='index.html?replytocom=472674#respond' data-commentid="472674" data-postid="126" data-belowelement="comment-472674" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to Maggie'>Reply</a>				</div><!-- .reply -->
