				<div class="comment-body"><p>I&#8217;m kind of curious as to why the Hugo award is the shape of a rocket and not something else since the Hugo awards categories are both sci fi and fantasy.</p>
</div>

				<div class="reply">
				<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='index.html?replytocom=518016#respond' data-commentid="518016" data-postid="126" data-belowelement="comment-518016" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to Cameron Miller'>Reply</a>				</div><!-- .reply -->
