				<div class="comment-body"><p>The 2019 Hugo Awards will be presented at the <a href="https://dublin2019.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">2019 World Science Fiction Convention</a> in Dublin, Ireland. The 2019 Hugo Awards will be administered by the 2019 Worldcon committee. The Hugo Awards are not administered by the Hugo Awards web site, but by the individual Worldcon committees. For more information, see the <a href="https://dublin2019.com/hugo-awards-wsfs/the-hugo-awards/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">2019 Hugo Awards web page</a> at the 2019 Worldcon web site.</p>
</div>

