				<div class="comment-body"><p>Hugo Awards are not awarded by a committee or board of directors or executive by fiat. They are presented in the categories listed here on our web site, and works have to be nominated by and voted upon by the members of the World Science Fiction Convention. So you can&#8217;t just &#8220;give a trophy to Elon Musk because I think his rocket is cool looking.&#8221;</p>
